content: Abbreviation from Godzilla/ field forms (Electrofishing and Netting)
Defaults to reading each line as a “1” if nothing is entered.  But you can also use this to record, for example, “75” of a given species or length
Text.  Defaults to not a mortality, if you write anything in this field, it will show that that fish is a mort or dead.  Typically people will record this a “y” or “1”
From drop down list in Godzilla
Alphanumeric field- 50 characters, not case sensitive
Numeric.  “0” (unmarked), “1” (marked).  You don’t have to write anything in the field.  If left blank it is assumed a “0”
label: Field
